    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change priority for social housing guidance to make all veterans eligible",
        "additional_details": "We believe that these men and women risked their lives to protect the lives of each and every one of us in this country and that we as a nation owe them the decency to look after them now as they did us.",
        "background": "Change guidance for local authorities on priority for social housing to make all veterans of our armed forces eligible for priority allocation of this housing. We want to help the people that served and have risked their life for the country. We think it's about time we give them something back.",
